data.description: Completely remodeled 3 bedroom / 2 bathroom home.  House sits on a large corner lot with fenced in backyard.  This house has just been updated with new floors, paint, vanities, toilets, fans, cabinets, granite countertops.  Also has newer style windows and a sunroom with lots of windows.  A must see!!!!! Room dimensions are approximate and should be verified prior to submitting an offer.
